{"tid":2300151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"交大家一個識手搖妹妹既方法...","createTime":"2020-11-25T09:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T10:58:26.000Z","uid":172709,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"26fd084579bfc55687e04b754be388ae1dcc9224","tid":2300151,"uid":172709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:38:10.000Z","msg":"早排去幫襯一間手搖黃店（邊間唔講）<br />\n見到入邊個手搖妹妹勁可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我有個衝動拎野飲既時候俾左廿蚊貼士佢<br />\n佢一收到個下對眼發光咁 好似前世未收過咁多貼士咁<br />\n個刻我就知今次得米喇 如是者我隔日就幫襯佢一次<br />\n每次都俾成廿蚊貼士佢 慢慢佢開始記得我叫開咩野飲<br />\n就係前日 我見時機成熟喇 就揸左我架林寶去接佢放工<br />\n問佢一唔一齊食晚飯佢答應左<br />\n就係咁 佢而家做左我女朋友了<br />\n希望可以幫到大家都識到個鐘意既妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7a96cac52a4bbc6fff0d66c6cf729af4ef1c9e","tid":2300151,"uid":113335,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:39:58.000Z","msg":"on99 第一日直接揸林寶去接佢咪搞掂"},{"pid":"7bd5160363d69e36d99b98f668b905bbe89e74d5","tid":2300151,"uid":172709,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a7a96cac52a4bbc6fff0d66c6cf729af4ef1c9e","tid":2300151,"uid":113335,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:39:58.000Z","msg":"on99 第一日直接揸林寶去接佢咪搞掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:42:31.000Z","msg":"唔靠俾貼士呢招絕技點溝手搖妹妹呀......"},{"pid":"3d1a9ab82e2d637f61947b426ea276b2510d7737","tid":2300151,"uid":371039,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:49:39.000Z","msg":"0.5/10<br />\n有望重作"},{"pid":"822f6ebfb420f7e7d7e0c834f8c6f43580a72955","tid":2300151,"uid":371558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d157b74650646c841a83c702b291e6dd43d8abac","tid":2300151,"uid":360907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:49:59.000Z","msg":"我第一